dct_title_s: West Indies/ engraved by G.W. Boynton. [copy 1]
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Inset map: Bermudas. Scale [ca. 1:700 000]. "Entered according to Act of Congress in the year 1838 by T.G. Bradford in the ... District Court of Massachusetts." Prime meridian: Washington. Scale in miles. From T.G Bradford's Illustrated atlas ... Boston : Weeks, Jordan, and Co. ; New York : Wiley and Putnam, [1838].
